headline.print_headline: Five-Star Oman, UAE Qualify for Gulf Cup Semi-Finals
headline.main: Five-Star Oman, UAE Qualify for Gulf Cup Semi-Finals

lead_paragraph: Substitute Said Al-Ruzaiqi grabbed a 16-minute hat-trick as Oman reached the semi-finals of the Gulf Cup with a 5-0 thrashing of Kuwait on Thursday, while holders the United Arab of Emirates also reached the last four.
